vidends?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes, many massive companies on the TSE do pay regular dividends. However, the real, tangible return for domestic investors is often deeply complicated by the rapid inflation and severe devaluation of the local currency, which can quickly erase the purchasing power of the dividend payment."}}]}];
